<section class="page-header">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <p>Answers to what customers ask us most.</p>
</section>

<section class="section faq-section" data-reveal>
  <div class="faq-list">

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h2>
        <button type="button" class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-1">
          What are your delivery times?
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-item__answer" id="faq-answer-1" hidden>
        <p>Orders within major cities typically arrive in 3-5 business days. Other locations may take 5-7 business days. You will receive a tracking link once your order ships.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h2>
        <button type="button" class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-2">
          Can I return or exchange an item?
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-item__answer" id="faq-answer-2" hidden>
        <p>Yes, unworn items with original tags can be exchanged within 7 days of delivery. Please reach out via WhatsApp or email to start the process.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h2>
        <button type="button" class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-3">
          How do I know what size to order?
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-item__answer" id="faq-answer-3" hidden>
        <p>Each product page includes a size guide. If you are unsure between two sizes, message us on WhatsApp with your measurements and we will help you choose.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h2>
        <button type="button" class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-4">
          What payment methods do you accept?
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-item__answer" id="faq-answer-4" hidden>
        <p>We accept bank transfer and cash on delivery in most cities. Payment details are confirmed at checkout.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h2>
        <button type="button" class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-5">
          Do you ship internationally?
          <span class="faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-item__answer" id="faq-answer-5" hidden>
        <p>At this time we ship within Pakistan only. International shipping is being planned for the future.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="faq-cta">
    <p>Still have a question?</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</section>
